":"Akari","body":"Why are you trying to make me smile?\nI just want you to leave me alone!\nGo away!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":209,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"Hagumi","body":"... She just wanted to be left alone...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":14,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"band3-014-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"Kanon","body":"We were going there for... almost a month...\nMaybe we should give her some space...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":14,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"band3-014-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"Kanon-san's right. It's what she wants, after all.\nAny more than this, we'd just be bothering her.\nWe'll just have to wait-","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"band3-014-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"No.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-014-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"Kokoro.\nI know you're not used to setbacks like this, I understand it must be tough. But you need to think about Akari...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"band3-014-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"A setback would mean we're not making progress. But I think we are. I think Akari just isn't being true to her feelings, and doesn't even know it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-014-016-2","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"As the great bard did say, \"play out the play!\"","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"band3-014-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"... Sigh. Sure.\nNot willing to call it a setback, huh.\nI'm pretty sure we should be holding off, but...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"band3-014-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"(More than anything, I just...\nI can't take this heavy atmosphere...)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"pui01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"band3-014-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"... Hmm? Hmm hmm hmm?\nI wasn't done watching yet...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-014-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"(It's not like Kokoro to stare glumly out the window.\n... She must still be worried about Akari.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"band3-014-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"Hmm... We're not even rehearsing any more, it's boring. I guess I could pick up where I left off with this...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"band3-014-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"Hey, what's that?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-014-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"Ah!!\nY-you made me jump...\nYou never talk to me in class like this.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"band3-014-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"Is that wool?\nAre you making animals with it?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-014-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"Oh, yeah. It's sheep-wool felt.\nYou prick it with a needle like this to make shapes.\nSee?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"band3-014-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"A dog! That's a dog's tail, right?\nIt's wonderful!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-014-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"Yeah. I mean, it's a cat, but yeah.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"band3-014-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"My little sister really likes plushies, you know?\nI'm not any good at making them, but they seem to make her happy, at least.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"band3-014-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"Likes plushies... happy...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-014-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"......!!\nHey, how do you know she likes them?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-014-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"How...? I guess, I dunno...\nI give them to her, and she looks happy. And I know she likes plushies because, I mean, we live together.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"band3-014-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"You know... she likes them...\nI see. That does make sense.\nI need you to fill me in on all the details, here.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-014-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"What?\nWhat details? There's nothing else to it...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"band3-014-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"I've known her all her life, I know she likes fluffy animals, so I gave her one and she was pleased. That's all. Understand?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"band3-014-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"So you didn't know if she'd like your felt animal until you gave it to her, then?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-014-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"Yeah, I guess not.\nThat's the most important part of giving a gift, right?\nThinking up something the other person might enjoy.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"band3-014-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"I wonder what she might like, and \"What kind of things would she enjoy?\" I dunno, maybe it's just me being a big sister.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"band3-014-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"Telling you like this might be hard to understand, huh.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"band3-014-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"No, I completely understand!!\nThank you so much!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-014-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"R-right, okay. You understand.\nWell that's... good, then.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"band3-014-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"I've realized... that I haven't given any thought to what Akari might like herself.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-014-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"Everything we've done so far has been my own ideas making people happy. I just assumed that everyone liked the same things that I did.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-014-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"But that's not true, is it.\nEveryone has their own things that they like, their own reasons to be happy!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-014-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"You say it like it's a grand revelation, but I'm pretty sure that's just common knowledge...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"band3-014-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"(... Or maybe it isn't. Knowing it isn't the same as acting on it, and coming to terms with it like this isn't something just anyone could do...)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"band3-014-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"Thank you!!\nI think I've come to terms with something very important today, all thanks to you!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-014-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"No, thank you. I think this is the first time we've actually had a real conversation together.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"band3-014-048","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"It's a little embarrassing, after this wonderful talk we've had, but 